<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	<title>学员证书查询数据库</title>
	{{> assets}}
	<style>
		body {
			min-height: 100vh;
			background: url("bg.png") round ;
			display: flex;
			align-items: center;
			justify-content: center;
			font-family: "Microsoft YaHei", sans-serif;
		}

		.query-container {
			background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
			border-radius: 15px;
			padding: 40px 30px;
			max-width: 400px;
			width: 100%;
			box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
			text-align: center;
		}

		.query-container h2 {
			margin-bottom: 30px;
			font-weight: 600;
		}

		.form-control {
			margin-bottom: 20px;
			height: 45px;
			padding: 0 10px;
			font-size: 16px;
			width: 100%;
			box-sizing: border-box;
		}

		.btn-query {
			width: 100%;
			height: 45px;
			font-size: 16px;
		}

		.note {
			margin-top: 20px;
			text-align: left;
			font-size: 14px;
			color: #555;
		}

		.athlete-left {
			position: absolute;
			bottom: 0;
			left: 0;
			width: 180px;
		}

		.athlete-right {
			position: absolute;
			bottom: 0;
			right: 0;
			width: 150px;
		}

		@media (max-width: 768px) {
			.athlete-left,
			.athlete-right {
				display: none;
			}
		}
	</style>
</head>
<body>
	<div class="query-container">
		<h2>学员证书查询数据库</h2>
		<form id="queryForm">
			<input type="text" class="form-control" id="queryInput" placeholder="编号（必填）" required>
			<button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-query">查询</button>
		</form>
		<div class="note">
			注意：<br>
			1. 查询证书需经权属人同意<br>
			2. 证书查询结果不得用于违背权属人意愿之用途
		</div>
	</div>

	<script>
		const form = document.getElementById("queryForm");
		const input = document.getElementById("queryInput");

		form.addEventListener("submit", function(e) {
			e.preventDefault(); // 阻止表单默认提交
			const queryValue = input.value.trim();
			if (queryValue) {
				// 跳转到 /result?q=编号
				window.location.href = `/result?q=${encodeURIComponent(queryValue)}`;
			} else {
				alert("请输入编号！");
			}
		});
	</script>
</body>
</html>
